# Personal Agent Runtime

Copy this file to `.agents/local/personal_config.md` and fill in values for
your own machine. Do not commit the copied personal file.

Before training, evaluation, or remote debugging, read:
`.agents/rules/remote-training-sop.md`

Before changing or repairing Mutagen sync, read:
`.agents/rules/mutagen-sync-sop.md`

Use these local bindings with those SOPs:

- SSH alias: `<ssh-alias>`
- Local project path: `<local-project-path>`
- Remote host project path: `<remote-project-path>`
- Remote host bind-mount path: `<remote-bind-mount-path>`
- Container name: `<container-name>`
- Container workspace path: `<container-workspace-path>`
- Python environment bin path: `<python-env-bin-path>`
- Mutagen session name: `<mutagen-session-name>`
